text: Barnes Dlamini is the president of the Swaziland Federation of Trade Unions (SFTU). Barnes was unanimously elected president at the SFTU congress in 2009, after having served at its vice president for four years. Barnes is also the president of the Swaziland United Democratic Front. == References == Category:Swazi trade unionists Category:Trade union leaders Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
